Global Cordless Electric Screwdriver Market Insights
Cordless Electric Screwdriver Market size was valued at USD 5.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 8.4 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Cordless Electric Screwdriver Market Overview
The global cordless electric screwdriver market was valued at approximately USD 1.2 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 2.3 billion by 2032, growing at a CAGR of 7.1%. This growth is driven by the increasing adoption of cordless power tools, advancements in battery technology, and a rising trend in DIY projects and home renovations. The market's expansion is further supported by the demand for lightweight, ergonomically designed tools that offer convenience and efficiency for both professional and residential users.

